@ballsoup I really like the people graphics! The color palette is good imo - for the color of the blue in the same text you can probably make it either a lighter blue (since smaller text looks darker), increase the size (may be inconsistent), or slightly darken the purpleish you use

- you may want to put health and care on the same line so one doesn't have to think about what they mean separated
- make "class size IS limited to" ‚Üí "limited to" since if you're going to use "is" you'd need to use "the" at the beginning (i think)
